"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640375391,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"NNfStd8AFbqmJ5N0KQJH0-gy8w4-mk8-V3PGipcHw7k\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0CFFeA7A8B00a496922D01790D271537dc4C3D3b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Oi9h0vcEm_IQF-IzFLRK7W5cqyo4I5wk51oeqxfQIuo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"gPK0jvvFvqJbvA7eYqnHxD2bp6wxE_Aozh0FMqr1plA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"NM2J5HYI_xDGZpPJpOY137_QExuoUyqfAz2yyINhQE5KO4yJunD0AJlDrDxde8NSTkX9Gw-YMEUwXfgz6E3Vtw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x542b7524b5cd910db4e4aafb3ef64c8731b80ad506816a55dd44386bf4b063e02842560e260556712c0ce747bb34cb053d58afa10b31f6c75b0aad4cc2cf37851c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Oi9h0vcEm_IQF-IzFLRK7W5cqyo4I5wk51oeqxfQIuo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"gPK0jvvFvqJbvA7eYqnHxD2bp6wxE_Aozh0FMqr1plA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi